snippet.textDisplay: If this was a “camera review” then the blown highlights would be disqualifying for the S20 Ultra. Instead what this was was a happy gadget enthusiast’s video on his enthusiastic first impressions. I’m right there with you. I love tech and new gadgets and the ability to record 8K is exciting. But camera comparison is not just pure resolution. The resolution is given. We knew that. The comparison should have included highlights/shadows clipping, color reproduction, noise. Also I know you wanted to get the video out very quickly but you should have taken a look at the recording and narrated the video while truly observing the differences instead of giving immediate and truly irrelevant impressions.
snippet.textOriginal: If this was a “camera review” then the blown highlights would be disqualifying for the S20 Ultra.
